Nice car.
好车。

67
00:02:10,880 --> 00:02:11,880
What seems to be the problem?
出了什么问题？

68
00:02:11,880 --> 00:02:12,880
I don't know.
我不知道。

69
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:13,880
I don't know.
我不知道。

