This stupid old car started being white smoke and it just died on me.
这辆破旧的老车开始冒白烟，然后就熄火了。

82
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,560
Luckily I managed to start it up and drive it here.
幸好我设法启动它开到了这里。

83
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:33,520
What do you think it is?
你觉得是什么问题？

84
00:02:33,520 --> 00:02:34,720
Not sure yet.
还不确定。

85
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:38,720
How about you pop the hood and we could take a look?
你打开引擎盖，我们看看怎么样？

86
